ne\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1375}, {\"ngram\": \"the continent\", \"from\": 1380, \"to\": 1393}, {\"ngram\": \"astronomy\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1404}, {\"ngram\": \"the past decade\", \"from\": 1450, \"to\": 1465}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is largely, though not entirely, a result of South Africa's status as co-host, with Australia, of what will be the world's largest radio telescope, the Square Kilometre Array (SKA), operated and managed by theSquare Kilometre Array Observatory.\", \"from\": 1468, \"to\": 1717, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1518, \"end\": 1530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.107131372962577e-17, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 1557, \"end\": 1566, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999999975325409, \"rank\": 2.335592589578991e-09, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a result\", \"from\": 1506, \"to\": 1514}, {\"ngram\": \"co\", \"from\": 1543, \"to\": 1545}, {\"ngram\": \"host\", \"from\": 1546, \"to\": 1550}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's largest radio telescope\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1619}, {\"ngram\": \"the Square Kilometre Array\", \"from\": 1621, \"to\": 1647}, {\"ngram\": \"SKA\", \"from\": 1649, \"to\": 1652}, {\"ngram\": \"theSquare Kilometre Array Observatory\", \"from\": 1679, \"to\": 1716}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Its first phase is set for completion in 2027; its precursor, the MeerKAT telescope, is already makinghuge contributionsto both South African and international science.\", \"from\": 1718, \"to\": 1886, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Its first phase\", \"from\": 1718, \"to\": 1733}, {\"ngram\": \"completion\", \"from\": 1745, \"to\": 1755}, {\"ngram\": \"its precursor\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1778}, {\"ngram\": \"the MeerKAT telescope\", \"from\": 1780, \"to\": 1801}, {\"ngram\": \"both South African and international science\", \"from\": 1841, \"to\": 1885}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Additional SKA dishes will be located in eight other African countries: Ghana, Zambia, Madagascar, Botswana, Namibia, Kenya, Mauritius and Mozambique.\", \"from\": 1887, \"to\": 2037, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1959, \"end\": 1964, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ghana\", \"score\": 0.9999999997749001, \"rank\": 2.2498080375491138e-10, \"text\": \"Ghana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ghana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ghana\"}, {\"begin\": 1966, \"end\": 1972, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\", \"score\": 0.9999999960618879, \"rank\": 3.9379656465501995e-09, \"text\": \"Zambia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\"}, {\"begin\": 1974, \"end\": 1984, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Madagascar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.573869963670849e-14, \"text\": \"Madagascar\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Madagascar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Madagascar\"}, {\"begin\": 1986, \"end\": 1994, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 1.065843447556034e-12, \"text\": \"Botswana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\"}, {\"begin\": 1996, \"end\": 2003, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Namibia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.679517816260244e-15, \"text\": \"Namibia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Namibia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Namibia\"}, {\"begin\": 2005, \"end\": 2010, \"title\": \"http